  <div class="newsletter-signup__intro">
    <strong>Stay on top of Drupal AI development — delivered daily.</strong>
    <p>
      The Daily Digest is an AI-generated summary of the last 24 hours of activity across the
      <a href="https://www.drupal.org/project/ai">Drupal AI initiative</a> — covering merged patches,
      open issues, contributor activity, and what's blocking progress. Two editions are available:
      one written for <strong>developers</strong> with technical detail, and one for
      <strong>executives</strong> focused on strategic progress and delivery milestones.
      <br />You can <a href="/ai-dashboard/daily-digest">browse recent digests here</a>.
    </p>
  </div>

